<p>To enhance the quality of life of local residents and to disseminate the important message of sports and exercise in all social classes, Macau Sports Development Board organises on a monthly basis "Sports for All Day" in various social communities.in order to promote residents’ participation in sports and to achieve the goal of lifelong exercise. </p><p><a href="http://www.sport.gov.mo/en/pa/sportdaytimetable/type/item/id/3750">http://www.sport.gov.mo/en/pa/sportdaytimetable/type/item/id/3750</a></p>